  "data": {
    "description": "<p>You can now equip [Blade] tagged items. This skill is effective while you are equipped with a [Blade] in the [Hand Slot]. You can also equip a [Magic Stone] in the [Hand slot].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(SR 2): You gain a + 1 bonus to [Evasion] and [Resistance].</p>\n<p>(SR 3): You gain a + [INT Mod] bonus to your [Physical Defense].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A battle style that combines magic stones with a blade instead of a staff to activate magic. If you master it, you can acquire the power of defense that can stand on the front line even though you are a magic attack class.</p>",
